# backend/requirements.in — human-readable dependency ranges.
#
# N1 policy: this is the source of truth. `backend/requirements.txt` is
# regenerated from this file via:
#
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file=backend/requirements.txt \
#       backend/requirements.in
#
# Docker and CI install with `pip install --require-hashes` against the
# generated lockfile. Any drift between `.in` and `.txt` fails CI.

